OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778186665
OL,3,C150-year-old mattress company enters
OL,4,Cadministration
OL,6,FMore than 70 people have been made
OL,7,Fredundant after a mattress and bed
OL,8,Fmanufacturer in Wiltshire entered
OL,9,Fadministration.
OL,11,FAirsprung has produced beds and
OL,12,Fmattresses from its Trowbridge factory
OL,13,Ffor more than 150 years.
OL,15,FThe company has also produced beds for
OL,16,Fhotels and filling for sports stadium
OL,17,Fseating under brands Gainsborough and
OL,18,FAirofreem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
