OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778186665
OL,3,C150-year-old mattress company enters
OL,4,Cadministration
OL,6,FTheir Canal Road factory site - the
OL,7,Fsize of 18 football pitches - can
OL,8,Fproduce more than two thousand
OL,9,Fmattresses a day.
OL,11,FAdministrators from PwC said the
OL,12,Fcompany had faced years of difficult
OL,13,Ftrading conditions and months of
OL,14,Fincreasing cashflow challenges,
OL,15,Fleaving directors with "no choice" but
OL,16,Fto place the company in administration.
OL,18,F71 of the company's 202 employees have
OL,19,Fbeen made redundant.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778186665
OL,3,C150-year-old mattress company enters
OL,4,Cadministration
OL,6,F"It's very sad that this well-known
OL,7,Fbusiness with 150 years of history and
OL,8,Ficonic brands within the mattress and
OL,9,Fbed industry has had to go into
OL,10,Fadministration," said Edward Williams,
OL,11,Fjoint administrator.
OL,13,F"We know that this is an unsettling
OL,14,Ftime for everyone impacted and we will
OL,15,Fsupport employees through the
OL,16,Fredundancy process."
OL,18,FRemaining employees will be kept on
OL,19,Fwhile interest in the business is
OL,20,Fexplored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778186665
OL,3,C150-year-old mattress company enters
OL,4,Cadministration
OL,6,FAirsprung's CEO and Director Tean
OL,7,FDallaway said it was "very sad and
OL,8,Fdisappointing" that the business had
OL,9,Fentered administration.
OL,11,F"I would like to sincerely thank our
OL,12,Fcustomers and suppliers for their
OL,13,Fsupport over many years, and most
OL,14,Fimportantly our employees for their
OL,15,Fdedication, professionalism, and hard
OL,16,Fwork," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
